data.description: Extensively renovated, move-in ready home.  Located in sought after and top rated SHOREWOOD school district. Home boasts: 4 bedrooms, 3 FULL baths, and 2,026+/- sq.ft. to spread out in. Large master suite with vaulted ceiling & private en-suite.  Property has modern amenities & updates, but care appears to have been taken to preserve the original character of the home (hardwood floors, built in cabinetry, etc.).  Large patio in back. Short distance to several nearby parks & UW - Milwaukee. Per seller, updates include: kitchen, bathrooms, furnace, exterior siding / paint, roof, windows, light fixtures, new garage, hardwood floors, new concrete, etc. See also private remarks.
